                    <tr>
                      <td valign="top" height="100%"><font face="arial" size="2" color="#000000"><span class="spnMessageText" id="msg"> 1) Are regen items such as zlandicars heart worth it and do effects stack? (e.g. with an item with aura of battle on it)<br /><br />2) I "heard" a while back that wearing a haste item confirs the haste on the pet? Any truth in this?<br /><br />3) If there was any ONE must have item except a circlet of shadow, what should it be?<br /><br />-=-=-<br /><br />Zlandicar's Heart rocks.  I just got mine at 56th.   I could solo the Rockhoppers before, but with this and lich, I wasn't constantly worrying if I was getting too low on health.  The 'always-on' regen on it is well worth the 20K I spent on it.  Your health will go down, but not fast.<br /><br />Haste will not transer to pet.<br /><br />I think the Circlet of Shadow is a convienece, and perhaps a life saver in the right situation, and I plan on getting one.  But not real soon.  You can do with out it.</span id="msg"></font><br><br></td>
