                      <td valign="top" height="100%"><font face="arial" size="2" color="#000000"><span class="spnMessageText" id="msg"> Musta haves are effects, you pick the effects that are best for me its AE4/AH4/BA4 and insta invis.  SH and MP4 are nice and i would like them but the first 4 effects are our bread and butter.  The sooner I got rid of my zheart the sooner I become a better player, I started taking more risks and quit being such a pansey, when i got 2 at low health I didn't FD because "ohh I got regen" instead I jsut killed them both.  Zheart is a crutch and an overpriced one at that.  No item is a must have BUT those first 4 will make a major difference.</span id="msg"></font><br><br></td>
